Help command is split into many
different help commands. This makes
code hard to read and long-winded.

design as a single help command
can provide help for many different
commands.

for note to be valid, note must be empty.
This then causes data to not reload.

Solve by setting default note to nonempty
string.

The original edit function from AB3 searches by index, which is
not intuitive. Additionally, it only accounts for one type of person
with limited attributes.

We expanded to different categories of person, specific for our niche
target group, dog cafe owners.

I implemented a search by name function into edit and also expanded the
edit function to allow edit of the different categories of people, namely
supplier, staff, maintainer, while keeping the original functionality intact.
